main event: Multiple witnesses reported seeing unidentified flying objects in Redding, California on multiple occasions, displaying high speeds and unusual flight patterns.
interesting points: The objects were described as having a whitish color and moving without any sound,Some witnesses reported that the objects changed altitude and direction rapidly,At least two observations were made at the Redding airport, with the sightings lasting several minutes each,One witness described the objects as having a circular shape and a tail-like structure,It was noted that the objects did not resemble any conventional aircraft.
witness description: residents and workers at the Redding airport
